"Detects the features enabled by the compiler. This option is appended by "
"default to ``cpu-baseline`` if ``-march``, ``-mcpu``, ``-xhost``, or ``/"
"QxHost`` is set in the environment variable ``CFLAGS`` unless ``cpu-baseline-"
"detect`` is ``disabled``."
msgstr ""

